<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Bootcamp Acceptance</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #3d016f;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background-color: #3d016f;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .program-details {
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Congratulations!</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <p>Dear <%= applicantName %>,</p>

        <p>We're thrilled to inform you that you've been accepted into our Tech Internship Bootcamp for <%= track %>! Your portfolio and application demonstrated the passion and potential we look for in our candidates.</p>

        <div class="program-details">
            <h3>Program Details:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Start Date: <%= startDate %></li>
                <li>Duration: <%= duration %></li>
                <li>Track: <%= track %></li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <h3>Next Steps:</h3>
        <ol>
            <li>Complete your enrollment by <%= enrollmentDeadline %></li>
            <li>Submit required documentation</li>
            <li>Attend orientation on <%= orientationDate %></li>
        </ol>

        <p>Please confirm your participation by clicking the button below within 48 hours:</p>
        
        <a href="<%= confirmationLink %>" class="button">CONFIRM PARTICIPATION</a>

        <p>Welcome to the team!</p>

        <p>Best regards,<br>
        Rhedge Studios Tech Bootcamp Team</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>Â© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Rhedge Studios. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
